1
00:00:00,020 --> 00:00:05,080
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:10,190
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,190 --> 00:00:15,330
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,330 --> 00:00:22,750
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:30,710
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,710 --> 00:00:35,570
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:40,270
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:49,630
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,930 --> 00:00:54,280
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,380
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,710 --> 00:01:03,400
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,970
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,460 --> 00:01:10,110
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:14,710
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:20,060
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,860
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:26,480
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 52 =

20
00:01:48,460 --> 00:01:51,020
Executing people

21
00:01:51,180 --> 00:01:52,660
is the last thing I want to do.

22
00:01:54,340 --> 00:01:55,260
I believe

23
00:01:56,020 --> 00:01:57,780
those who should be executed according to laws

24
00:01:58,620 --> 00:02:01,300
might not deserve it.

25
00:02:03,860 --> 00:02:04,940
I always think

26
00:02:05,940 --> 00:02:07,100
every man has his faults.

27
00:02:10,300 --> 00:02:11,978
Isn’t it better to mend and atone

28
00:02:13,300 --> 00:02:15,500
than to punish them severely?

29
00:02:17,220 --> 00:02:18,900
But it’s not easy to mend.

30
00:02:20,340 --> 00:02:21,260
Things you’ve done,

31
00:02:22,300 --> 00:02:23,420
people you’ve hurt

32
00:02:24,660 --> 00:02:27,140
and the hostility you’ve brought

33
00:02:27,140 --> 00:02:28,340
to the one you care for the most...

34
00:02:29,900 --> 00:02:31,820
You must try your best to make it up,

35
00:02:32,500 --> 00:02:36,020
even if your efforts turn out to be of no avail.

36
00:02:44,500 --> 00:02:45,420
The baby prince...

37
00:02:48,740 --> 00:02:50,660
I named him Zhao Xuan

38
00:02:53,140 --> 00:02:54,060
in my heart.

39
00:04:50,517 --> 00:04:51,557
His Majesty has arrived.

40
00:05:23,157 --> 00:05:23,962
Look who this is.

41
00:05:28,340 --> 00:05:29,360
Father.

42
00:05:29,514 --> 00:05:30,112
Father?

43
00:05:31,980 --> 00:05:33,140
He said Father.

44
00:05:34,060 --> 00:05:34,860
Father.

45
00:05:35,060 --> 00:05:36,060
= Zhao Zongshi’s Son Zhao Zhongzhen =
When I was little,

46
00:05:36,060 --> 00:05:37,660
did I also call you like that?

47
00:05:41,780 --> 00:05:43,180
But let me teach you.

48
00:05:43,700 --> 00:05:44,900
This is Grandpa.

49
00:05:45,300 --> 00:05:46,380
Not father.

50
00:05:48,180 --> 00:05:48,860
Huirou.

51
00:05:50,660 --> 00:05:52,340
Give Zhongzhen to his wet nurse.

52
00:05:52,346 --> 00:05:53,500
The banquet is starting.

53
00:05:53,700 --> 00:05:55,340
Don’t make him cry.

54
00:05:55,760 --> 00:05:57,456
But he likes to play with me.

55
00:05:59,733 --> 00:06:00,586
Okay. Okay.

56
00:06:00,613 --> 00:06:01,312
Okay. Okay.

57
00:06:01,413 --> 00:06:02,560
Don’t cry.

58
00:06:13,870 --> 00:06:15,550
When Zuixinglai was at this age,

59
00:06:17,210 --> 00:06:19,090
he called Father more clearly.

60
00:06:20,890 --> 00:06:22,170
And he recognized people.

61
00:06:23,570 --> 00:06:25,170
He never called anyone else

62
00:06:25,890 --> 00:06:27,090
Father.

63
00:06:46,530 --> 00:06:47,250
Huirou.

64
00:06:48,450 --> 00:06:50,450
Give this to your mother.

65
00:06:50,970 --> 00:06:53,290
She always likes it since she was little.

66
00:07:07,250 --> 00:07:08,010
Your Majesty.

67
00:07:10,250 --> 00:07:11,330
I have something

68
00:07:11,810 --> 00:07:13,770
to tell you

69
00:07:14,250 --> 00:07:15,410
since the royal relatives are present.

70
00:07:16,850 --> 00:07:18,810
You accepted awards from officials

71
00:07:19,010 --> 00:07:20,610
and sold them information of the imperial harem.

72
00:07:21,490 --> 00:07:24,530
= Zhang Chengzhao =
You’ll be flogged and expelled.

73
00:07:28,490 --> 00:07:29,170
My...

74
00:07:29,650 --> 00:07:30,330
My...

75
00:07:31,970 --> 00:07:33,410
My parents died early.

76
00:07:34,570 --> 00:07:36,610
I was castrated at eight.

77
00:07:37,690 --> 00:07:38,450
If I go back to the clan,

78
00:07:38,770 --> 00:07:40,450
I won’t be accepted.

79
00:07:41,330 --> 00:07:44,090
I don’t know what life is like out there.

80
00:07:45,610 --> 00:07:46,530
Mr. Zhang.

81
00:07:47,050 --> 00:07:47,890
Mr. Zhang.

82
00:07:48,650 --> 00:07:49,410
I’m begging you.

83
00:07:50,730 --> 00:07:51,970
Punish me in whatever way,

84
00:07:53,090 --> 00:07:54,450
expect expelling me.

85
00:07:56,250 --> 00:07:57,090
If...

86
00:07:59,530 --> 00:08:01,370
If I can’t be forgiven

87
00:08:02,170 --> 00:08:03,370
or I can’t stay anymore,

88
00:08:05,730 --> 00:08:07,010
please just kill me,

89
00:08:07,010 --> 00:08:08,050
Mr. Zhang.

90
00:08:09,130 --> 00:08:10,730
That’ll be better than

91
00:08:11,610 --> 00:08:12,770
being expelled, despised

92
00:08:13,130 --> 00:08:15,890
or reviled.

93
00:08:17,210 --> 00:08:18,090
Mr. Zhang.

94
00:08:19,250 --> 00:08:20,130
Mr. Zhang.

95
00:08:20,890 --> 00:08:21,850
I’m begging you.

96
00:08:22,890 --> 00:08:23,850
I’m begging you!

97
00:08:42,730 --> 00:08:43,570
Fine.

98
00:08:44,930 --> 00:08:46,930
You’ll be punished.

99
00:08:47,770 --> 00:08:49,130
You’ll be flogged, too.

100
00:08:50,770 --> 00:08:52,250
But I’ll keep you.

101
00:08:57,530 --> 00:08:58,730
You’re close to

102
00:08:58,770 --> 00:09:00,890
Xia Song and Madam Zhang’s maids.

103
00:09:01,450 --> 00:09:03,770
I think you know more about them.

104
00:09:04,850 --> 00:09:05,770
Work for me

105
00:09:06,370 --> 00:09:08,490
and let’s handle Aunt Jia’s house first.

106
00:09:11,722 --> 00:09:12,965
Thank you, Mr. Zhang.

107
00:09:14,416 --> 00:09:15,450
Thank you, Mr. Zhang!

108
00:09:16,506 --> 00:09:17,685
Thank you, Mr. Zhang.

109
00:09:20,420 --> 00:09:22,980
Madam Miao is elegant and virtuous.

110
00:09:23,540 --> 00:09:24,540
She behaves well,

111
00:09:25,900 --> 00:09:27,980
and gave birth to children.

112
00:09:28,700 --> 00:09:30,020
After Prince Yong was born,

113
00:09:30,580 --> 00:09:32,460
she declined the promotion several times.

114
00:09:39,380 --> 00:09:41,820
Now, Princess Fukang is fourteen.

115
00:09:42,540 --> 00:09:44,980
Her husband is widely recognized

116
00:09:44,980 --> 00:09:47,220
throughout the imperial court.

117
00:09:48,860 --> 00:09:50,133
= Cao Yi’s Son Cao Ping =
Taking the chance of this banquet,

118
00:09:51,060 --> 00:09:52,540
His Majesty and I agree

119
00:09:54,020 --> 00:09:56,700
to promote Princess Fukang’s mother Madam Miao

120
00:09:57,340 --> 00:09:58,620
to imperial concubine.

121
00:10:04,620 --> 00:10:07,180
We’re marrying our daughter soon.

122
00:10:07,660 --> 00:10:08,820
Don’t decline it again.

123
00:10:20,180 --> 00:10:24,060
Thank you, Your Majesty and Your Highness.

124
00:10:33,180 --> 00:10:34,540
Besides Madam Miao,

125
00:10:36,620 --> 00:10:38,220
another madam

126
00:10:39,060 --> 00:10:40,260
deserves to be promoted, too.

127
00:10:44,500 --> 00:10:46,180
Madam Zhang has served His Majesty for years.

128
00:10:47,420 --> 00:10:49,060
She gave birth to three princesses.

129
00:10:49,980 --> 00:10:51,420
When she prayed for her daughter,

130
00:10:52,060 --> 00:10:53,340
she asked to get demoted.

131
00:10:53,940 --> 00:10:55,140
She hasn’t been promoted in years.

132
00:10:56,380 --> 00:10:57,460
On the day of coup,

133
00:10:58,100 --> 00:10:59,380
she wanted to defend His Majesty,

134
00:10:59,940 --> 00:11:01,660
even though she was weak.

135
00:11:02,700 --> 00:11:04,340
His Majesty is grateful,

136
00:11:04,940 --> 00:11:06,780
and wants to award her.

137
00:11:08,700 --> 00:11:09,460
So,

138
00:11:10,500 --> 00:11:11,980
why don’t we promote her to the consort

139
00:11:13,140 --> 00:11:16,180
as the reward for her?

140
00:11:26,220 --> 00:11:27,500
We survived the coup,

141
00:11:27,900 --> 00:11:30,500
because you dispatched guards well.

142
00:11:31,820 --> 00:11:32,820
In case of reward,

143
00:11:33,780 --> 00:11:35,060
you should be the first to be awarded.

144
00:11:37,100 --> 00:11:38,580
Thank you, Your Majesty.

145
00:11:39,500 --> 00:11:40,940
But I’m already the Empress.

146
00:11:41,500 --> 00:11:43,700
I can’t be promoted anymore.

147
00:11:45,220 --> 00:11:47,060
Besides, I’m your wife.

148
00:11:47,740 --> 00:11:49,140
I can’t repay you kindness.

149
00:11:50,100 --> 00:11:52,820
I was just doing my job.

150
00:11:54,060 --> 00:11:56,300
I don’t dare to ask for any award.

151
00:12:15,940 --> 00:12:17,020
Don’t follow me.

152
00:12:40,220 --> 00:12:41,580
You’re leaving town today?

153
00:12:42,380 --> 00:12:43,380
I’m seeing somebody off

154
00:12:43,500 --> 00:12:44,380
and I’ll be right back.

155
00:12:54,740 --> 00:12:56,740
= Bitao =

156
00:13:15,740 --> 00:13:17,340
Why did you suddenly offer

157
00:13:18,060 --> 00:13:19,500
to promote Madam Zhang?

158
00:13:24,860 --> 00:13:26,460
Officials argued over that for six months.

159
00:13:27,260 --> 00:13:28,780
Madams also talked about it.

160
00:13:29,420 --> 00:13:30,780
People were guessing.

161
00:13:34,220 --> 00:13:35,140
I don’t think

162
00:13:36,020 --> 00:13:37,060
we can stop them from guessing

163
00:13:37,780 --> 00:13:39,460
unless we make a decision.

164
00:13:54,380 --> 00:13:56,020
It’s true that

165
00:13:56,540 --> 00:13:57,860
Madam Zhang serves you best

166
00:13:59,660 --> 00:14:00,740
and she has entered the palace for years.

167
00:14:01,620 --> 00:14:02,740
It’s understandable

168
00:14:03,940 --> 00:14:04,980
to promote her to consort.

169
00:14:38,940 --> 00:14:39,780
Huaiji.

170
00:14:41,660 --> 00:14:42,460
Why?

171
00:14:43,580 --> 00:14:44,460
I thought...

172
00:14:46,300 --> 00:14:47,020
I didn’t want to

173
00:14:47,460 --> 00:14:49,260
marry Li Wei.

174
00:14:51,260 --> 00:14:52,260
But today,

175
00:14:53,340 --> 00:14:54,620
when I saw

176
00:14:55,540 --> 00:14:57,060
my marriage made Mother promoted

177
00:14:58,660 --> 00:14:59,740
and she was happy.

178
00:15:00,900 --> 00:15:02,620
I was a bit happy, too.

179
00:15:04,620 --> 00:15:05,500
But Madam Zhang

180
00:15:05,500 --> 00:15:06,900
was promoted to consort,

181
00:15:07,180 --> 00:15:08,180
senior to Mother.

182
00:15:08,860 --> 00:15:09,740
Why?

183
00:15:13,060 --> 00:15:14,860
Madam Miao is gentle and mild.

184
00:15:15,660 --> 00:15:17,100
She never competes with Madam Zhang.

185
00:15:19,420 --> 00:15:20,340
She doesn’t.

186
00:15:21,220 --> 00:15:22,260
But I’m not convinced.

187
00:15:29,860 --> 00:15:31,300
Aunt Jia and Maid Xu

188
00:15:31,420 --> 00:15:33,700
took poison together,

189
00:15:35,020 --> 00:15:37,860
saying they quarreled.

190
00:15:38,980 --> 00:15:39,780
I don’t believe

191
00:15:39,780 --> 00:15:41,260
it has nothing to do with Madam Zhang.

192
00:15:42,580 --> 00:15:44,140
They both work for her.

193
00:15:44,620 --> 00:15:46,780
One is her trusted follower.

194
00:15:47,660 --> 00:15:48,420
The other...

195
00:15:49,020 --> 00:15:49,980
The other one

196
00:15:50,740 --> 00:15:52,140
framed me up for cursing my sister

197
00:15:52,220 --> 00:15:53,660
with a doll.

198
00:15:57,300 --> 00:15:59,100
Two people died in the Pavilion of Luan.

199
00:16:00,140 --> 00:16:01,220
But it was not investigated.

200
00:16:02,340 --> 00:16:03,340
Then Madam Zhang

201
00:16:03,340 --> 00:16:04,420
was promoted.

202
00:16:05,260 --> 00:16:06,740
I know Father is seduced by her.

203
00:16:07,180 --> 00:16:08,860
But why does Her Highness also flatter her?

204
00:16:10,020 --> 00:16:11,740
Can she truly be so arrogant?

205
00:16:15,860 --> 00:16:16,780
I’m hungry.

206
00:16:22,940 --> 00:16:24,420
If you go back to the banquet,

207
00:16:25,020 --> 00:16:26,340
you can still enjoy the crab soup.

208
00:16:27,460 --> 00:16:28,380
I’m not going back.

209
00:16:29,220 --> 00:16:30,380
I’m still angry.

210
00:16:31,820 --> 00:16:32,620
Fine.

211
00:16:34,100 --> 00:16:35,100
But...

212
00:16:35,460 --> 00:16:36,980
We can only go to the kitchen

213
00:16:37,060 --> 00:16:38,500
and see if there are cold steamed buns.

214
00:16:39,540 --> 00:16:41,460
If there aren’t any,

215
00:16:42,460 --> 00:16:43,500
I’ll have to

216
00:16:43,620 --> 00:16:45,220
roast some sweet potatoes for you.

217
00:17:15,340 --> 00:17:17,340
I played this song for many times.

218
00:17:17,820 --> 00:17:18,660
But it’s the first time

219
00:17:18,660 --> 00:17:20,020
to cooperate with someone so well.

220
00:17:20,460 --> 00:17:21,420
Thank you, Miss Ying.

221
00:17:36,420 --> 00:17:37,140
Your Highness.

222
00:17:38,140 --> 00:17:39,140
Sweet potatoes are ready.

223
00:17:40,100 --> 00:17:41,060
Have one

224
00:17:41,140 --> 00:17:42,140
and you won’t feel so cold.

225
00:17:47,540 --> 00:17:48,820
These days, Zhang Chengzhao has been

226
00:17:48,820 --> 00:17:50,220
working for Mr. Zhang.

227
00:17:51,420 --> 00:17:52,420
You can have some more rest

228
00:17:52,420 --> 00:17:53,260
without anxiety.

229
00:17:54,780 --> 00:17:55,620
After having the sweet potatoes,

230
00:17:56,260 --> 00:17:57,220
I’ll walk you back.

231
00:18:01,220 --> 00:18:04,420
Huaiji, sit beside me.

232
00:18:10,260 --> 00:18:11,060
I can’t.

233
00:18:13,820 --> 00:18:14,580
Huaiji.

234
00:18:16,460 --> 00:18:19,300
I’m tired and cold.

235
00:18:21,100 --> 00:18:22,140
I want to lean on you.

236
00:18:52,740 --> 00:18:53,940
I’m going to learn harp.

237
00:19:02,340 --> 00:19:03,860
Go tell her I don’t want it!

238
00:19:04,580 --> 00:19:05,820
Funny!

239
00:19:07,020 --> 00:19:07,900
She and Zhang Maoze

240
00:19:07,900 --> 00:19:09,060
killed Aunt Jia.

241
00:19:09,060 --> 00:19:09,620
Does she think

242
00:19:09,620 --> 00:19:11,220
she can draw me over with such a promotion?

243
00:19:11,860 --> 00:19:12,940
Not to mention a consort,

244
00:19:13,260 --> 00:19:14,980
I don’t even care for

245
00:19:14,980 --> 00:19:15,860
the status of empress.

246
00:19:16,220 --> 00:19:17,020
Bihan.

247
00:19:23,580 --> 00:19:24,340
Leave us.

248
00:19:36,860 --> 00:19:37,580
Bihan.

249
00:19:42,780 --> 00:19:43,620
Your Majesty.

250
00:19:44,820 --> 00:19:48,220
Jewels, treasures and titles.

251
00:19:49,020 --> 00:19:50,140
I like all of them.

252
00:19:51,140 --> 00:19:52,780
But I only want them from you.

253
00:19:53,260 --> 00:19:55,460
I don’t need any reward from anyone else.

254
00:20:04,980 --> 00:20:05,740
Your Majesty.

255
00:20:08,140 --> 00:20:08,940
Don’t try to

256
00:20:08,940 --> 00:20:10,060
reason me out.

257
00:20:11,060 --> 00:20:12,100
I won’t listen.

258
00:20:13,940 --> 00:20:15,620
I hate your empress.

259
00:20:16,980 --> 00:20:18,220
Whatever you say

260
00:20:18,940 --> 00:20:21,060
will only make me hate her more.

261
00:20:37,820 --> 00:20:38,700
Bihan.

262
00:20:40,460 --> 00:20:42,420
When did I ever reason you out?

263
00:20:43,740 --> 00:20:44,460
You...

264
00:20:45,340 --> 00:20:46,700
You’re always a girl.

265
00:20:47,180 --> 00:20:49,220
A naught girl.

266
00:20:51,100 --> 00:20:52,060
I don’t want to

267
00:20:52,060 --> 00:20:53,260
make you a mature woman.

268
00:20:54,540 --> 00:20:56,060
Neither a reasonable woman

269
00:20:57,620 --> 00:20:58,940
or a stupid one.

270
00:21:02,020 --> 00:21:04,060
They... they say I’m a bad woman.

271
00:21:05,500 --> 00:21:06,580
I’m so bad.

272
00:21:07,620 --> 00:21:09,020
Do you still like me?

273
00:21:15,370 --> 00:21:16,850
I don’t like any bad guys.

274
00:21:17,620 --> 00:21:18,700
You’re overbearing.

275
00:21:18,736 --> 00:21:20,300
But you tolerated Lantiao.

276
00:21:22,380 --> 00:21:23,700
If you didn’t know

277
00:21:23,740 --> 00:21:26,140
Yaoyao died because of her jealousy,

278
00:21:27,580 --> 00:21:29,340
you would be nice to her baby, too.

279
00:21:30,100 --> 00:21:31,580
You love babies.

280
00:21:32,620 --> 00:21:33,820
But without her,

281
00:21:34,740 --> 00:21:36,300
Yaoyao would have been alive.

282
00:21:37,100 --> 00:21:38,700
She must be a gorgeous

283
00:21:38,700 --> 00:21:39,660
and good girl.

284
00:21:42,340 --> 00:21:44,460
If you want her to learn literature,

285
00:21:44,860 --> 00:21:46,300
she will learn it

286
00:21:46,340 --> 00:21:47,260
very carefully.

287
00:21:48,300 --> 00:21:49,580
If she likes dancing,

288
00:21:49,740 --> 00:21:51,500
Aunt Jia and I will teach her.

289
00:21:53,317 --> 00:21:54,260
I’m not convinced.

290
00:21:56,020 --> 00:21:57,140
Why did all my families

291
00:21:57,140 --> 00:21:58,180
leave me alone?

292
00:21:59,500 --> 00:22:01,340
I’ve even lost Aunt.

293
00:22:03,220 --> 00:22:04,860
Her Highness instigated Zhang Maoze.

294
00:22:04,900 --> 00:22:06,140
They framed up Aunt

295
00:22:06,300 --> 00:22:07,740
and got Lantiao dead, too.

296
00:22:09,740 --> 00:22:10,500
Don’t...

297
00:22:14,700 --> 00:22:15,940
Don’t hate others.

298
00:22:17,340 --> 00:22:18,340
It’s my fault.

299
00:22:22,820 --> 00:22:26,900
Because I didn’t take care of my biological mother,

300
00:22:26,900 --> 00:22:28,500
I’m now punished by heaven.

301
00:22:29,900 --> 00:22:30,940
Zuixinglai,

302
00:22:32,540 --> 00:22:34,140
Yaoyao, Chuyue

303
00:22:35,140 --> 00:22:36,180
and Youwu

304
00:22:39,180 --> 00:22:40,220
went to heaven to take care of her.

305
00:22:40,220 --> 00:22:40,860
Your Majesty.

306
00:22:41,260 --> 00:22:42,220
Your Majesty, what’s wrong?

307
00:22:42,420 --> 00:22:43,940
Somebody! Somebody!

308
00:22:44,900 --> 00:22:45,740
It’s okay.

309
00:22:46,540 --> 00:22:47,900
Let me have some rest.

310
00:22:49,220 --> 00:22:50,220
For a little moment.

311
00:23:16,620 --> 00:23:17,540
Bihan.

312
00:23:19,140 --> 00:23:20,540
I’m not arguing with you.

313
00:23:21,740 --> 00:23:23,740
I won’t advice you not to hate people.

314
00:23:24,020 --> 00:23:25,620
But I ask you

315
00:23:26,580 --> 00:23:28,860
not to hurt anyone because of hatred

316
00:23:29,700 --> 00:23:31,420
or provoke the Empress deliberately

317
00:23:31,420 --> 00:23:32,460
to embarrass her.

318
00:23:32,900 --> 00:23:33,780
Except that,

319
00:23:34,420 --> 00:23:35,780
I’ll get you

320
00:23:36,260 --> 00:23:38,020
whatever you want

321
00:23:39,500 --> 00:23:41,140
