322
00:24:03,820 --> 00:24:06,260
Thank you for promoting me to noble consort.

323
00:24:07,380 --> 00:24:08,660
Your Majesty, please show some mercy.

324
00:24:10,740 --> 00:24:13,220
Aunt raised me, instructed me

325
00:24:13,740 --> 00:24:14,740
and defended me.

326
00:24:16,300 --> 00:24:18,140
She had an engagement when she was young.

327
00:24:18,900 --> 00:24:21,340
The late Emperor gave Xia Song another wife

328
00:24:21,340 --> 00:24:23,060
but Aunt lived a poor life alone.

329
00:24:24,860 --> 00:24:26,140
I knew what she wanted.

330
00:24:27,340 --> 00:24:28,580
She’s dead.

331
00:24:29,620 --> 00:24:30,940
I can’t avenge her.

332
00:24:33,540 --> 00:24:36,820
Please ask someone to escort her coffin

333
00:24:38,020 --> 00:24:39,460
to Xia Song

334
00:24:39,500 --> 00:24:40,820
and let him handle the funeral.

335
00:24:46,020 --> 00:24:47,020
Noble consort?

336
00:24:52,940 --> 00:24:54,100
It’s okay.

337
00:24:56,860 --> 00:24:59,180
I don’t need excuses for your future promotion.

338
00:25:02,020 --> 00:25:03,700
I’ll tell the empress.

339
00:25:03,900 --> 00:25:06,340
I guess she’ll agree.

340
00:25:09,140 --> 00:25:10,500
As for Jia Yulan,

341
00:25:13,220 --> 00:25:14,980
I’ll have her sent to Xia Song,

342
00:25:16,860 --> 00:25:17,740
considering her loyalty to you.

343
00:25:28,700 --> 00:25:29,500
Get the carriage ready.

344
00:25:30,900 --> 00:25:32,380
Send His Majesty back to his palace.

345
00:25:40,300 --> 00:25:41,060
I...

346
00:25:41,980 --> 00:25:44,340
I’m going to stay here tonight.

347
00:25:46,540 --> 00:25:47,340
I...

348
00:25:48,700 --> 00:25:50,740
I don’t dare to hold you from work.

349
00:25:52,900 --> 00:25:53,860
Besides,

350
00:25:55,220 --> 00:25:56,420
physicians checked on me.

351
00:25:58,100 --> 00:25:58,940
I can...

352
00:26:00,900 --> 00:26:03,020
I can hardly have babies for you anymore.

353
00:26:04,060 --> 00:26:05,580
So, it’s meaningless

354
00:26:05,580 --> 00:26:06,500
to keep you at my place.

355
00:26:08,620 --> 00:26:09,700
If I want

356
00:26:11,500 --> 00:26:13,260
some other treasure,

357
00:26:13,460 --> 00:26:14,500
I’ll ask you for it.

358
00:26:17,140 --> 00:26:17,900
Today,

359
00:26:20,220 --> 00:26:21,540
I’ll see you off.

360
00:26:33,260 --> 00:26:37,380
= Xia Mansion =

361
00:26:42,940 --> 00:26:47,100
= Xia Song, courtesy name Ziqiao =

362
00:26:47,100 --> 00:26:47,860
Mr. Xia.

363
00:26:49,780 --> 00:26:51,380
As Noble Consort Zhang requested,

364
00:26:52,060 --> 00:26:53,220
His Majesty asked me

365
00:26:54,020 --> 00:26:56,380
to escort Jia Yulan’s coffin to you.

366
00:26:57,220 --> 00:26:58,300
You’ll take care of

367
00:26:59,180 --> 00:27:00,860
her funeral.

368
00:27:03,860 --> 00:27:07,060
Thank you, Mr. Zhang.

369
00:27:11,540 --> 00:27:12,780
Jia Yulan is guilty.

370
00:27:14,260 --> 00:27:16,260
But she took care of Noble Consort Zhang for years

371
00:27:16,780 --> 00:27:18,060
