372
00:27:19,620 --> 00:27:20,700
It’s kind of His Majesty.

373
00:27:21,940 --> 00:27:24,540
And Noble Consort Zhang is promoted.

374
00:27:25,540 --> 00:27:26,900
There’ll be no more punishment.

375
00:27:38,460 --> 00:27:39,420
Noble Consort?

376
00:28:02,580 --> 00:28:07,580
I’m grateful to His Majesty

377
00:28:09,060 --> 00:28:11,660
