384
00:28:44,220 --> 00:28:47,220
Her properties have been confiscated.

385
00:28:48,180 --> 00:28:49,420
His Majesty gave a secret order that

386
00:28:49,740 --> 00:28:50,820
the money shall be used

387
00:28:51,460 --> 00:28:53,180
to run free schools in Qinghe County.

388
00:28:53,940 --> 00:28:57,660
The money will be used for charity.

389
00:28:59,860 --> 00:29:02,540
Maitreya Sect bewitched people

390
00:29:02,540 --> 00:29:03,820
and its members rebelled.

391
00:29:05,100 --> 00:29:07,020
In putting down the rebellion,

392
00:29:07,580 --> 00:29:08,980
His Majesty only killed their leaders

393
00:29:10,860 --> 00:29:12,620
instead of ordinary members.

394
00:29:14,060 --> 00:29:16,220
In the rebellion place,

395
00:29:17,540 --> 00:29:20,820
schools are built to pacify and educate people.

396
00:29:22,740 --> 00:29:23,500
Good.

397
00:29:25,020 --> 00:29:25,700
Good.

398
00:29:27,580 --> 00:29:29,020
I see.

399
00:29:31,340 --> 00:29:32,300
I see.

400
00:29:43,380 --> 00:29:45,820
His Majesty always admires your talent.

401
00:29:48,460 --> 00:29:50,420
When you defended our nation from Xixia,

402
00:29:50,940 --> 00:29:53,300
you made contributions to local people.

403
00:29:54,060 --> 00:29:55,780
His Majesty remembers that.

404
00:29:58,460 --> 00:29:59,820
He knows

405
00:30:00,100 --> 00:30:01,860
you’re obsessed in ancient characters.

406
00:30:02,860 --> 00:30:04,500
Even when you were busy

407
00:30:05,060 --> 00:30:06,300
in a battle,

408
00:30:06,820 --> 00:30:08,540
you studied on ancient proses

409
00:30:08,940 --> 00:30:10,180
before you went to bed.

410
00:30:11,260 --> 00:30:12,820
To buy antiques,

411
00:30:13,460 --> 00:30:15,140
you spent a lot of money.

412
00:30:16,380 --> 00:30:19,540
You’re not useless or evil

413
00:30:21,380 --> 00:30:24,140
as others think you are.

414
00:30:39,140 --> 00:30:43,420
Mr. Zhang, please wait a minute.

415
00:30:47,260 --> 00:30:48,540
Go to my study

416
00:30:48,540 --> 00:30:50,220
and get me the manuscripts.

417
00:31:11,460 --> 00:31:17,060
= Four Tones in Ancient Chinese Characters =

418
00:31:19,700 --> 00:31:20,940
In the past two decades,

419
00:31:23,380 --> 00:31:26,380
based on the knowledge I’ve learnt,

420
00:31:28,980 --> 00:31:30,780
I’ve collected ancient characters

421
00:31:33,740 --> 00:31:37,900
and written the books

422
00:31:38,780 --> 00:31:41,220
Four Tones in Ancient Chinese Characters.

423
00:32:18,900 --> 00:32:23,260
His Majesty is generous to me.

424
00:32:25,020 --> 00:32:27,060
I’m giving the books to him.

425
00:32:28,900 --> 00:32:32,420
I can’t repay His Majesty with mere books,

426
00:32:34,100 --> 00:32:37,540
but they will be helpful to later generations.

427
00:32:54,180 --> 00:33:00,020
= Xia Song died in 1051 A.D.
with a posthumous title Wenzhuang. =

428
00:33:05,020 --> 00:33:06,420
What snacks have you found?

429
00:33:06,420 --> 00:33:07,260
It took you so long.

430
00:33:08,340 --> 00:33:10,260
= Xiao Ye’er =
I nearly learnt the whole song.

431
00:33:17,740 --> 00:33:18,580
What happened?

432
00:33:19,100 --> 00:33:20,100
Someone slapped you?

433
00:33:21,740 --> 00:33:22,860
Don’t ask, Princess.

434
00:33:22,940 --> 00:33:23,940
It was my fault.

435
00:33:24,900 --> 00:33:26,180
Tell me what happened.

436
00:33:26,580 --> 00:33:27,780
You’re my maid.

437
00:33:28,100 --> 00:33:28,860
Even if you made a mistake,

438
00:33:28,940 --> 00:33:30,540
someone should tell Mother and me

439
00:33:30,660 --> 00:33:31,820
and we would punish you.

440
00:33:32,700 --> 00:33:33,860
She slapped you before telling us.

441
00:33:34,060 --> 00:33:35,220
She wasn’t humiliating you,

442
00:33:35,300 --> 00:33:36,540
but us.

443
00:33:37,660 --> 00:33:38,340
It was...

444
00:33:39,220 --> 00:33:40,660
Prince Consort Zhang’s uncle

445
00:33:40,660 --> 00:33:41,900
kidnapped this year’s principal graduate Feng Jing

446
00:33:41,900 --> 00:33:42,740
to his mansion

447
00:33:42,740 --> 00:33:44,180
and forced Feng Jing to marry his daughter.

448
00:33:44,260 --> 00:33:45,020
The other day,

449
00:33:45,020 --> 00:33:46,900
Madam Yu told you and Madam Miao.

450
00:33:47,260 --> 00:33:48,540
When I went to the Imperial Kitchen,

451
00:33:48,540 --> 00:33:49,300
I heard

452
00:33:49,300 --> 00:33:51,100
other maids are talking about it.

453
00:33:51,260 --> 00:33:52,260
I was so indiscreet that

454
00:33:52,260 --> 00:33:53,540
I talked with them.

455
00:33:54,020 --> 00:33:55,020
As we talked,

456
00:33:55,180 --> 00:33:55,980
we didn’t notice that

457
00:33:55,980 --> 00:33:57,380
someone entered the hall

458
00:33:57,460 --> 00:33:58,100
and heard us.

459
00:33:58,100 --> 00:33:59,220
She came in

460
00:33:59,220 --> 00:34:00,340
and slapped every one of us,

461
00:34:00,340 --> 00:34:02,420
saying she taught us to behave ourselves.

462
00:34:03,780 --> 00:34:04,660
Funny!

463
00:34:07,740 --> 00:34:09,300
It’s a scandal of Noble Consort Zhang.

464
00:34:10,020 --> 00:34:10,900
They did that,

465
00:34:11,100 --> 00:34:12,180
but allowed no one to gossip.

466
00:34:12,780 --> 00:34:13,940
Madam Yu told me.

467
00:34:14,380 --> 00:34:16,620
Officials laughed at them.

468
00:34:16,820 --> 00:34:18,220
Common people laughed at them, too.

469
00:34:18,740 --> 00:34:20,900
What? Can’t we laugh then?

470
00:34:22,140 --> 00:34:23,380
Madam Zhang used to be domineering.

471
00:34:23,740 --> 00:34:24,940
And now she’s a noble consort.

472
00:34:25,260 --> 00:34:26,580
His Majesty spoils her.

473
00:34:27,260 --> 00:34:28,020
= Jiaqing Zi =
I heard

474
00:34:28,060 --> 00:34:28,820
His Majesty was going to relegate Xiaosong

475
00:34:28,940 --> 00:34:30,300
because of her.

476
00:34:30,540 --> 00:34:31,540
If it’s true,

477
00:34:31,820 --> 00:34:33,260
she’ll be more domineering.

478
00:34:33,660 --> 00:34:34,660
Relegate Xiaosong?

479
00:34:35,580 --> 00:34:37,140
Father loves his writings.

480
00:34:39,500 --> 00:34:41,380
What did he do to annoy her?

481
00:34:41,980 --> 00:34:43,380
The coronation thing.

482
00:34:43,780 --> 00:34:45,420
All titled concubines

483
00:34:45,580 --> 00:34:47,780
used to decline a ceremony and accept the title.

484
00:34:48,140 --> 00:34:48,860
Song thought

485
00:34:48,900 --> 00:34:50,780
Noble Consort Zhang would do the same thing

486
00:34:51,140 --> 00:34:52,660
when he wrote the coronation decree.

487
00:34:52,820 --> 00:34:53,940
So, without asking for permission,

488
00:34:54,300 --> 00:34:56,020
he stamped on the coronation decree directly,

489
00:34:56,140 --> 00:34:57,820
sealed it and gave it to Noble Consort Zhang.

490
00:34:59,980 --> 00:35:00,820
And then?

491
00:35:01,180 --> 00:35:01,940
Then...

492
00:35:02,060 --> 00:35:04,020
Noble Consort Zhang burned with anger.

493
00:35:04,140 --> 00:35:05,260
She ran to the Hall of Happiness and Tranquility

494
00:35:05,380 --> 00:35:06,740
and threw the decree on the ground.

495
00:35:07,340 --> 00:35:08,340
She said,

496
00:35:08,940 --> 00:35:10,700
“I wouldn’t have been so neglected

497
00:35:10,780 --> 00:35:12,300
even if I married a rural landlord.

498
00:35:12,860 --> 00:35:14,100
Your Majesty, are you

499
00:35:14,100 --> 00:35:15,180
