500
00:35:15,340 --> 00:35:17,220
or is your subordinate humiliating you?”

501
00:35:19,180 --> 00:35:20,980
How dared she talk to Father like that!

502
00:35:22,020 --> 00:35:22,900
Jiaqing Zi.

503
00:35:26,340 --> 00:35:27,860
When did you go there

504
00:35:28,460 --> 00:35:29,300
and even saw

505
00:35:29,300 --> 00:35:30,980
how Noble Consort Zhang talked to His Majesty.

506
00:35:39,220 --> 00:35:41,420
Since Noble Consort Zhang was promoted,

507
00:35:41,780 --> 00:35:43,980
she gave orders to all bureaus directly

508
00:35:44,300 --> 00:35:46,580
without telling you, Your Highness.

509
00:35:47,260 --> 00:35:48,980
When chiefs of all bureaus see

510
00:35:48,980 --> 00:35:50,380
she’s been greatly promoted.

511
00:35:51,100 --> 00:35:52,020
His Majesty must be loving her.

512
00:35:52,180 --> 00:35:53,580
They don’t dare to mess up with her.

513
00:35:54,540 --> 00:35:55,500
You know what?

514
00:35:55,860 --> 00:35:57,780
In less than one month,

515
00:35:58,060 --> 00:36:00,020
she used more than twice you have used.

516
00:36:00,620 --> 00:36:02,580
She’s far more than exceeding the standard.

517
00:36:05,460 --> 00:36:07,060
The new chief maid for her,

518
00:36:07,060 --> 00:36:07,900
Aunt Li.

519
00:36:07,900 --> 00:36:10,180
She’s said to be capable in her evaluation.

520
00:36:11,180 --> 00:36:12,700
Why is she so out of line?

521
00:36:14,260 --> 00:36:15,500
Go get Officer Ren to me.

522
00:36:17,340 --> 00:36:19,660
No capable maids

523
00:36:19,740 --> 00:36:22,140
want to work for Noble Consort Zhang.

524
00:36:22,860 --> 00:36:24,140
If someone wants to go,

525
00:36:24,380 --> 00:36:25,740
she must be after some benefits.

526
00:36:26,660 --> 00:36:27,460
Besides,

527
00:36:27,580 --> 00:36:29,500
when she was a mere lady,

528
00:36:29,660 --> 00:36:31,260
she only used Aunt Jia.

529
00:36:31,660 --> 00:36:33,020
His Majesty had no choice,

530
00:36:33,540 --> 00:36:34,620
but to let her do it.

531
00:36:35,380 --> 00:36:36,300
Now,

532
00:36:36,980 --> 00:36:38,780
Aunt Jia is dead,

533
00:36:38,780 --> 00:36:39,900
because of the bad things she did.

534
00:36:40,420 --> 00:36:42,180
Who could stop

535
00:36:42,380 --> 00:36:43,580
other bad guys from working for her?

536
00:36:49,580 --> 00:36:51,820
To make His Majesty happy,

537
00:36:51,940 --> 00:36:53,460
you even offered to promote her.

538
00:36:53,900 --> 00:36:55,700
She’s directly a noble consort.

539
00:36:56,580 --> 00:36:59,020
Who else dares to mess up with her?

540
00:37:01,820 --> 00:37:03,260
After Aunt Jia died,

541
00:37:04,460 --> 00:37:05,700
it was a hard job

542
00:37:05,980 --> 00:37:07,300
to pick another maid for Noble Consort Zhang.

543
00:37:07,900 --> 00:37:10,820
I’m afraid Officer Ren didn’t sleep for nights

544
00:37:11,300 --> 00:37:13,500
before he finally realized that

545
00:37:13,980 --> 00:37:15,860
Aunt Li had contacted with

546
00:37:16,060 --> 00:37:19,060
Noble Consort Zhang’s family before.

547
00:37:19,660 --> 00:37:21,940
Aunt Li would be the best candidate.

548
00:37:22,540 --> 00:37:23,740
So, Officer Ren just

549
00:37:23,740 --> 00:37:25,340
wanted to complete the mission quickly.

550
00:37:30,020 --> 00:37:31,820
You sound smart.

551
00:37:33,860 --> 00:37:36,220
I didn’t know

552
00:37:36,460 --> 00:37:37,900
you had such a glib tongue.

553
00:37:39,060 --> 00:37:40,900
And how did you know

554
00:37:41,260 --> 00:37:42,620
so many messy things?

555
00:37:44,580 --> 00:37:45,700
I swear

556
00:37:45,940 --> 00:37:47,340
I haven’t asked around.

557
00:37:48,260 --> 00:37:51,020
After Madam Zhang was promoted,

558
00:37:51,460 --> 00:37:52,780
many madams

559
00:37:52,980 --> 00:37:53,940
and chiefs of bureaus

560
00:37:53,940 --> 00:37:55,780
