562
00:37:57,340 --> 00:37:59,580
They couldn’t help complaining to me first.

563
00:38:01,020 --> 00:38:02,380
Maybe they mistakenly think

564
00:38:02,380 --> 00:38:03,740
I’m your trusted follower

565
00:38:04,180 --> 00:38:05,980
