566
00:38:09,020 --> 00:38:10,140
What are you talking about?

567
00:38:10,980 --> 00:38:11,860
Mistakenly think?

568
00:38:14,500 --> 00:38:15,780
Are you complaining that

569
00:38:16,460 --> 00:38:17,940
I’m not close enough to you?

570
00:38:21,380 --> 00:38:22,300
A trusted follower

571
00:38:22,900 --> 00:38:25,180
can certainly borrow power

572
00:38:25,180 --> 00:38:26,180
from her master

573
00:38:26,500 --> 00:38:28,060
while no one else dares to complain.

574
00:38:28,460 --> 00:38:29,580
This is a real trusted follower.

575
00:38:32,380 --> 00:38:34,940
You’re advising me with allegory.

576
00:38:35,940 --> 00:38:36,780
Oh, I see.

577
00:38:37,780 --> 00:38:40,580
If all chiefs of bureaus are wrong,

578
00:38:40,740 --> 00:38:41,940
the mistake

579
00:38:42,260 --> 00:38:43,420
was first made by me.

580
00:38:45,460 --> 00:38:46,980
I will reflect on myself,

581
00:38:47,180 --> 00:38:49,100
and discuss with His Majesty for a remedy.

582
00:38:49,460 --> 00:38:50,180
All right?

583
00:39:02,740 --> 00:39:03,860
Well, I know.

584
00:39:06,380 --> 00:39:07,900
Promoting Madam Zhang

585
00:39:08,740 --> 00:39:09,620
to solve

586
00:39:09,620 --> 00:39:11,380
previous problems,

587
00:39:11,860 --> 00:39:13,980
stop people from arguing and discussing,

588
00:39:14,460 --> 00:39:15,140
and especially stop them

589
00:39:15,140 --> 00:39:17,260
from guessing how Lantiao died

590
00:39:18,740 --> 00:39:20,260
isn’t a perfect way.

591
00:39:20,460 --> 00:39:21,540
There’ll be more trouble.

592
00:39:23,380 --> 00:39:25,060
But since the coup,

593
00:39:26,100 --> 00:39:27,740
everyone has been waiting for his defense.

594
00:39:30,180 --> 00:39:32,860
More people complain about him for injustice.

595
00:39:34,180 --> 00:39:35,380
In this case,

596
00:39:35,740 --> 00:39:37,100
His Majesty is too embarrassed.

597
00:39:41,380 --> 00:39:42,460
I’ll think about it.

598
00:39:43,700 --> 00:39:44,940
If Noble Consort Zhang

599
00:39:45,300 --> 00:39:46,540
still lives such a life,

600
00:39:47,380 --> 00:39:48,780
I’ll go discuss with His Majesty.

601
00:40:03,940 --> 00:40:04,620
Eat them.

602
00:40:08,180 --> 00:40:09,340
But Madam Miao said

603
00:40:09,340 --> 00:40:10,900
we must kneel for 24 hours

604
00:40:10,900 --> 00:40:11,780
and have nothing to eat.

605
00:40:13,020 --> 00:40:14,100
Mother is always softhearted.

606
00:40:14,460 --> 00:40:15,580
How will she let you

607
00:40:15,580 --> 00:40:17,100
eat nothing for the whole day?

608
00:40:18,500 --> 00:40:19,860
I took the food

609
00:40:19,860 --> 00:40:20,740
in front of her.

610
00:40:20,940 --> 00:40:22,140
But she said nothing to stop me.

611
00:40:26,860 --> 00:40:27,860
Come on. Eat them.

612
00:40:28,540 --> 00:40:30,660
She just punished you to convince others.

613
00:40:37,580 --> 00:40:39,100
Princess, I swear.

614
00:40:39,140 --> 00:40:40,620
I wasn’t telling a lie.

615
00:40:40,860 --> 00:40:42,220
I wasn’t in the Hall of Happiness and Tranquility.

616
00:40:42,220 --> 00:40:43,940
But I heard that from the eunuchs.

617
00:40:44,180 --> 00:40:45,660
I trust you.

618
00:40:47,060 --> 00:40:48,540
Aunt Jia was a bit of a bully.

619
00:40:48,860 --> 00:40:50,220
But Aunt Li,

620
00:40:50,220 --> 00:40:50,940
who works for Noble Consort Zhang now,

621
00:40:50,940 --> 00:40:51,980
is a real bully.

622
00:40:52,460 --> 00:40:53,420
Princess, do you know?

623
00:40:53,660 --> 00:40:55,020
She even scolded Mr. Liang.

624
00:40:55,860 --> 00:40:57,940
What? She dared to bully Huaiji?

625
00:40:58,340 --> 00:40:59,940
I heard it from a eunuch, too.

626
00:41:00,340 --> 00:41:01,580
He went out of the palace with Mr. Liang,

627
00:41:01,580 --> 00:41:02,540
for some purchase.

628
00:41:02,780 --> 00:41:03,740
They came back late.

629
00:41:04,060 --> 00:41:05,900
His Majesty reviews proposals every night.

630
00:41:06,260 --> 00:41:07,700
So, they were in a hurry.

631
00:41:08,140 --> 00:41:10,140
When they passed Imperial Office Bureau,

632
00:41:10,300 --> 00:41:11,300
Noble Consort Zhang’s maids

633
00:41:11,300 --> 00:41:12,500
were blocking the gate

634
00:41:12,580 --> 00:41:13,460
with a cart of things.

635
00:41:13,940 --> 00:41:15,500
Mr. Liang tried to squeeze through,

636
00:41:15,700 --> 00:41:17,180
but Aunt Li shouted abuse.

637
00:41:17,860 --> 00:41:18,660
“In the cart are treasures

638
00:41:18,660 --> 00:41:20,180
you can’t even find in the palace.

639
00:41:20,340 --> 00:41:21,340
Don’t squeeze or knock them.

640
00:41:21,500 --> 00:41:22,420
If you break something,

641
00:41:22,500 --> 00:41:23,820
you can’t pay the price even if you die.”

642
00:41:24,540 --> 00:41:25,420
Aunt Li?

643
00:41:26,140 --> 00:41:27,220
She was the one who slapped me, too.

644
00:41:28,860 --> 00:41:31,260
But what were they bringing in

645
00:41:31,340 --> 00:41:32,460
that couldn’t even be found in the palace?

646
00:41:33,060 --> 00:41:34,540
Since she became the noble consort,

647
00:41:34,700 --> 00:41:36,300
she has contacted with more officials.

648
00:41:36,620 --> 00:41:38,180
Her maids often went out and came in.

649
00:41:38,340 --> 00:41:39,820
Who knows how many treasures she has got?

650
00:41:40,260 --> 00:41:42,540
When Zhang Maoze worked in Imperial Office Bureau,

651
00:41:42,780 --> 00:41:44,700
who dared to transfer things like that?

652
00:41:46,140 --> 00:41:47,060
I heard

653
00:41:47,340 --> 00:41:48,940
it was also Zhang Maoze

654
00:41:48,940 --> 00:41:50,260
who convicted Aunt Jia and Xu Lantiao.

655
00:41:50,980 --> 00:41:51,860
But look.

656
00:41:52,020 --> 00:41:52,940
He wasn’t awarded,

657
00:41:53,180 --> 00:41:54,540
but was sent away from the Capital.

658
00:41:55,140 --> 00:41:56,660
Everyone knows he’s been demoted.

659
00:41:57,180 --> 00:41:59,420
Father is getting more muddleheaded!

660
00:42:01,780 --> 00:42:02,860
Shush, Princess.

661
00:42:03,180 --> 00:42:04,420
How dare you complain about the Emperor?

662
00:42:04,980 --> 00:42:06,460
If Her Highness hears you,

663
00:42:07,180 --> 00:42:09,100
I’m afraid you’ll be grounded for a month.

664
00:42:09,460 --> 00:42:12,140
And we’ll have nothing to eat in a month.

665
00:42:13,780 --> 00:42:14,540
Wait.

666
00:42:16,180 --> 00:42:17,980
What treasure

667
00:42:18,740 --> 00:42:19,700
couldn’t even be found in the palace?

668
00:42:27,850 --> 00:42:37,490
♪ Loved you a gentleman yet got abandoned ♪

669
00:42:38,850 --> 00:42:47,170
♪ Peach blossoms color the city ♪

670
00:42:50,010 --> 00:42:54,730
♪ Spring breeze purified dusty memories ♪

671
00:42:55,730 --> 00:42:59,890
♪ The gate of the vast palace opens ♪

672
00:43:01,330 --> 00:43:06,810
♪ Bid farewell with wine after the glory ends ♪

673
00:43:06,810 --> 00:43:11,570
♪ Outside the city a beautiful world unveils ♪

674
00:43:15,250 --> 00:43:20,890
♪ Long-standing distance doesn’t alienate us ♪

675
00:43:20,890 --> 00:43:25,810
♪ Keep you company behind the gate ♪

676
00:43:26,290 --> 00:43:32,050
♪ Four seasons come and go ♪

677
00:43:32,050 --> 00:43:37,130
♪ We only have each other in this cage ♪

678
00:43:37,570 --> 00:43:42,490
♪ Wish to fly freely in the next life ♪

679
00:43:43,130 --> 00:43:47,970
♪ Willows turn green flowers red ♪

680
00:43:48,650 --> 00:43:53,810
♪ Sing aloud with wine ♪

681
00:43:54,330 --> 00:43:59,370
♪ Hold your hands and go home together ♪

682
00:43:59,890 --> 00:44:03,970
♪ Be a pair of swallows in the next life ♪

683
00:44:05,450 --> 00:44:10,090
♪ Build the nest and protect the nestlings ♪

684
00:44:11,090 --> 00:44:16,250
♪ The howling wind ♪

685
00:44:16,610 --> 00:44:20,690
♪ Woke me up from the dream ♪

686
00:44:22,170 --> 00:44:27,090
♪ Be a pair of swallows in the next life ♪

687
00:44:27,770 --> 00:44:32,970
♪ Build the nest and protect the nestlings ♪

688
00:44:33,410 --> 00:44:38,690
♪ The howling wind ♪

689
00:44:38,970 --> 00:44:43,850
♪ Woke me up from the dream ♪

690
00:44:44,450 --> 00:44:51,170
♪ Life is long yet joy is little ♪
